com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.support.permission.fragment

Class DynamicPermissionsFragment

  • java.lang.Object
    • Fragment
      • com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.support.fragment.DynamicFragment
        • com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.support.permission.fragment.DynamicPermissionsFragment
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SharedPreferences.OnSharedPreferenceChangeListener

    public class DynamicPermissionsFragment
extends DynamicFragment
    Base fragment class to show a list of required permissions in a recycler view. It will be used internally by the DynamicPermissionsActivity to request or manage permissions.
